data.name: ToolStripMenuItem24.ToolTipText
data.value: Sets the current date to a custom date within a user session. This feature is used in back dating or foward dating, for operations that require a different date other than the normal system date. After enabling this feature, all operations shall be dated on the custom date. Remember to log in afresh so as to resume the normal system date. NB. You can not end the day when this feature is enabled, log in afresh to be able to end the day
